    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Coherence of Augmented Iwasawa <span class="search-hit mathjax">Algebras</span>
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Timmins%2C+J">James Timmins</a>
      
