        &hellip;of the numerical scheme include point-wise mass conservation, energy stability, and pressure robustness. We prove that there exists a solution to the resulting nonlinear <span class="search-hit mathjax">algebraic</span> system in two and three spatial dimensions, and that this solution is unique in two spatial dimensions under a small data assumption. A priori error estimates are derived for both&hellip;
