        Model theoretic properties of dynamics on the Cantor set
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Eagle%2C+C+J">Christopher J. Eagle</a>, 
      
