    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Bounds on complexity of matrix multiplication away from CW tensors
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Homs%2C+R">Roser Homs</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Jelisiejew%2C+J">Joachim Jelisiejew</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Micha%C5%82ek%2C+M">Mateusz Michałek</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Seynnaeve%2C+T">Tim Seynnaeve</a>
      
