    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        A New Maximal Subgroup of $E_8$ in Characteristic $3$
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Craven%2C+D+A">David A. Craven</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Stewart%2C+D+I">David I. Stewart</a>, 
      
