    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Finiteness of Stationary Configurations of the Planar Five-vortex Problem
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Yu%2C+X">Xiang Yu</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Zhu%2C+S">Shuqiang Zhu</a>
      
