        3-Lie <span class="search-hit mathjax">Algebras</span>, Ternary Nambu-Lie <span class="search-hit mathjax">algebras</span> and link invariants
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
