      <span class="abstract-short has-text-grey-dark mathjax" id="2103.11301v1-abstract-short" style="display: inline;">
        &hellip;energy method and spectral analysis, we show that solution of the Cauchy problem tend time-asymptotically to linear diffusion waves around the constant ground state with <span class="search-hit mathjax">algebraic</span> decaying rates under certain conditions on the density-dependent pressure function.
        <a class="is-size-7" style="white-space: nowrap;" onclick="document.getElementById('2103.11301v1-abstract-full').style.display = 'inline'; document.getElementById('2103.11301v1-abstract-short').style.display = 'none';">&#9661; More</a>
